{"tid":1941646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係中東人眼中,ISIS唔係恐怖份子, 而係悍衛本土的自由義士","createTime":"2020-03-24T14:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T14:31:36.000Z","uid":353419,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b51e7cf6482821f0521804b66c2cda8f6f97aa28","tid":1941646,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:05:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.answering-islam.org/chinese/topic19/tc-19-398.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.answering-islam.org%2Fchinese%2Ftopic19%2Ftc-19-398.html&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=836844db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.answering-islam.org/chinese/topic19/tc-19-398.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國穆斯林中有13%認為，傷及平民的暴力事件許多時候、有時候或少部分是合理的，為捍衛伊斯蘭之故。皮尤研究2011年調查顯示，美國穆斯林中有19%表示親阿爾蓋達，此外另有研究指，支持恐怖主義的佔全球穆斯林人口15%以上。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkPVmTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkPVmTX.jpg&h=e98f2f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地一直覺得阿蓋達塔利班係恐怖份子，因為恐怖份子無差別襲擊。但係中東人眼中，所有西方國家的人都唔係無辜，認為佢地全是極權的幫兇。中東人認為美軍殺害自己子女，但無能力正面對抗美軍，唯有去敵國城市炸美軍的子女。<br />\n<br />\n係中東人眼中，阿蓋達唔係恐怖份子，而係幫佢地出番啖氣的英雄。究竟中東人受過咩逼迫，令佢地變到咁極進？值得大家深思"},{"pid":"d356b78e89008587ffe91fd6cc20365111e50887","tid":1941646,"uid":81190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"你想講啲咩？"},{"pid":"7d9cc31480130a769174760a9dce0f708dd6d2f7","tid":1941646,"uid":317956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"IS唔係阿蓋達"},{"pid":"7a60a760e188e4c3ced9b1e2052217e3a5013560","tid":1941646,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d356b78e89008587ffe91fd6cc20365111e50887","tid":1941646,"uid":81190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"你想講啲咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"我想同大家傾下中東人的心理，究竟佢地經歷過啲咩"},{"pid